Diamod Pattern:

Java program to display Diamond Pattern for different testcase:

Firstly, I have created a public class named DiamondPatternn.
I have defined main method to begin the execution.
I have created Scanner class to take input from the user.
I have initialized a variable n with zero.
I am asking user to enter the N value.
I am storing the value into the variable n given by the user.
I have created a printStarDiamond method and passing parameter n.
if,n<0 thenI am displaying to enter the positive number.
I declaring the temp variable a and initialized with 0.
I am creating for first half portion printing space, digit, new line
I am creatingfor second half portion printing space, digit, new line
Finally, I am displaying the Diamond pattern.

